data.description: Come see this well-maintained, beautiful two-story home minutes away from Lackland Air Force base. Open floor plan with lots of natural lighting. Perfect starter home or investor potential. Curb appeal beckons from the street as you step up to a darling front porch in front. The home has a second large living room on the 2nd floor equipped with a media room with a projector and a projector screen. Large bedrooms with like new carpeting. Two-car garage for vehicle storage and workbench space.
